<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Son Hatırlatma: Hesabınızı Aktif Edin - DK List</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24, #ff6b6b);
            animation: glow 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes glow {
            from { opacity: 0.5; }
            to { opacity: 1; }
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .final-warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4757 0%, #ff3838 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 71, 87, 0.3);
            animation: shake 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-2px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(2px); }
        }
        .countdown-timer {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2c3e50 0%, #34495e 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .days-count {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 10px 0;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .activation-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.4);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }
        .activation-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.6);
        }
        .missed-opportunities {
            background-color: #fff5f5;
            border: 2px solid #feb2b2;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .opportunity {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        .opportunity-icon {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e74c3c 0%, #c0392b 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin-right: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .last-chance-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fdcb6e 0%, #e17055 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(225, 112, 85, 0.3);
        }
        .social-proof {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .proof-item {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border: 2px solid #e74c3c;
        }
        .proof-number {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e74c3c;
        }
        .proof-label {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .urgency-bar {
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e74c3c 0%, #f39c12 50%, #e74c3c 100%);
            border-radius: 3px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            animation: loading 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        @keyframes loading {
            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }
            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🚨 DK List</h1>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 18px;">SON HATIRLATMA</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="final-warning">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">⚠️ HESABINIZ SİLİNEBİLİR!</h2>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">{{ username }}, bu son hatırlatmamız. Hesabınızı hemen aktif etmezseniz silinecektir.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="countdown-timer">
                <h3 style="margin: 0;">🕒 Kayıt Tarihinizden Bu Yana</h3>
                <div class="days-count">{{ daysSince }}</div>
                <p style="margin: 0;">GÜN GEÇTİ</p>
                <div class="urgency-bar"></div>
                <small>{{ registrationDate }} - Bugün</small>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="http://localhost:3000/auth/{{ activationToken }}" class="activation-button">
                    🔥 HESABIMI KURTAR
                </a>
                <p style="color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 10px;">
                    ⏱️ Son şansınız! Hemen aktif edin.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="missed-opportunities">
                <h3 style="color: #e74c3c; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    {{ daysSince }} Gün Boyunca Kaçırdıklarınız:
                </h3>
                
                <div class="opportunity">
                    <div class="opportunity-icon">📚</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Kişisel Kütüphane</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #666;">{{ daysSince }} gün boyunca kitaplarınızı organize edemediniz</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="opportunity">
                    <div class="opportunity-icon">⭐</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Kitap Değerlendirmeleri</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #666;">Okuduğunuz kitapları değerlendirip puan veremediniz</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="opportunity">
                    <div class="opportunity-icon">👥</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Sosyal Etkileşim</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #666;">Kitap severlerle tanışma ve sohbet fırsatını kaçırdınız</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="opportunity">
                    <div class="opportunity-icon">🎯</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Okuma Hedefleri</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #666;">2024 okuma hedefinizi belirleyip takip edemediniz</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="opportunity">
                    <div class="opportunity-icon">🏆</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Rozetler & Başarımlar</strong><br>
                        <small style="color: #666;">Okuma aktivitelerinizle rozetler kazanma şansını kaybettiniz</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="last-chance-box">
                <h3 style="margin: 0 0 15px 0;">🎁 SON ŞANS AVANTAJLARI</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">Hesabınızı bugün aktif ederseniz:</p>
                <ul style="text-align: left; display: inline-block; margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                    <li>🎯 Ücretsiz okuma hedefi koçluğu</li>
                    <li>📈 Gelişmiş istatistikler</li>
                    <li>🔔 Özel kitap önerileri</li>
                    <li>👑 Erken üye rozeti</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="social-proof">
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-number">15K+</div>
                    <div class="proof-label">Aktif Üye</div>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-number">75K+</div>
                    <div class="proof-label">Kitap</div>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-number">500+</div>
                    <div class="proof-label">Günlük Aktif</div>
                </div>
                <div class="proof-item">
                    <div class="proof-number">95%</div>
                    <div class="proof-label">Memnuniyet</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; padding: 20px; background-color: #fff5f5; border-radius: 10px;">
                <p style="color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">
                    ❗ Aktivasyon sorunu yaşıyorsanız derhal bize yazın: 
                    <a href="mailto:support@dklist.com" style="color: #e74c3c;">support@dklist.com</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>DK List</strong> - Son Hatırlatma</p>
            <p>Bu e-posta {{ email }} adresine gönderilmiştir.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.8;">
                © 2024 DK List. Bu hesap yakında silinebilir.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 